items.title: US SEC summons Gautam Adani, nephew Sagar in bribery case
items.description: Summons have been sent to Adani's Shantivan Farm residence in Ahmedabad and his nephew Sagar's Bodakdev residence in the same city for a reply to SEC within 21 days

items.title: As Mahayuti sweeps Maharashtra, Adani’s Dharavi project gains momentum
items.description: Adani-led Dharavi redevelopment hinges on state support for housing over a million residents
